<description>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;컴퓨터를 포맷하고 Boost 라이브러리중에 써봐야 될것이 있어서 다시 Boost를 설치하던 도중에&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:820px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F9958093359D35E9E103069&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/9958093359D35E9E10&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;1.PNG&quot; height=&quot;413&quot; width=&quot;820&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;Boost의 bootstrap을 실행 시키니 다음과 같은 에러가 발생한다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;무슨 에러인지 확인하기 위해 위에서 bootstrap.log파일을 확인하라고 하는거 같은데.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:820px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile6.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F999B9E3359D35E9E0AC24C&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/999B9E3359D35E9E0A&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;2.PNG&quot; height=&quot;159&quot; width=&quot;820&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;내용은 다음과 같다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;저 에러와 같이 yyacc.c라는 파일이 없다고 한다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;구글링을 해봐도 다 영어에다가 현재 내 경우와 다른거 같아서 제대로 해결이 안되서 방법을 생각하던중, Unreal엔진 소스 빌드도 원래 컴퓨터를 포맷하기 전에는 잘 빌드되다가 포맷 한 후에 빌드가 안된게 기억이 났다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;혹시 Visual C++ Runtime 라이브러리가 없어서 그런가 싶어서 확인을 해보니&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:820px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile9.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F99194E3359D35E9F15366F&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/99194E3359D35E9F15&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;3.PNG&quot; height=&quot;238&quot; width=&quot;820&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;Visual C++ 2015 버전만 설치되어 있지 않은걸 확인하고 설치를 하기로 했다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:820px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile27.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F9979263359D35E9F34B240&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/9979263359D35E9F34&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;4.PNG&quot; height=&quot;468&quot; width=&quot;820&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:480px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile1.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F9955753359D35E9F24BDAC&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/9955753359D35E9F24&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;5.PNG&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; width=&quot;480&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;..? 설치가 되지 않는다&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;x86 버전도 마찬가지로 되질 않는다..&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:820px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile5.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F9979B23359D35EA00D099E&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/9979B23359D35EA00D&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;6.PNG&quot; height=&quot;26&quot; width=&quot;820&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;imageblock&quot; style=&quot;display:inline-block;width:334px;;height:auto;max-width:100%&quot;&gt;&lt;img srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory&amp;fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile1.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F99C43E3359D35EA02ED026&quot; src=&quot;https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/99C43E3359D35EA02E&quot; filemime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; filename=&quot;6_1.PNG&quot; height=&quot;29&quot; width=&quot;334&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;그래서 우연치 않게 Autodesk 웹사이트에 직접적인 문제의 내용은 아니지만 런타임 라이브러리 문제에 관한 내용에서 위와 같은 문구를 보았다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;Boost 라이브러리가 설치가 안되는 이유가 뭘까..&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;해결 -&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;Boost 라이브러리를 설치 할 때 Windows 소스가 아닌 Linux 소스를 다운받은거 같다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;&quot;&gt;아무생각 없이 빨리 하려고 다운하다 보니 생긴 불상사 인데, 그래도 이런 삽질을 또 해서 새로운 사실을 알았다.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
